OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1782307135
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thu 9 Jul to Thu 23 Jul
OL,6,FHigh pressure patterns are looking
OL,7,Fslightly more likely than low pressure
OL,8,Fpatterns during the early part of this
OL,9,Fperiod, meaning a greater chance of
OL,10,Fsettled and drier than average
OL,11,Fconditions. There is still a chance of
OL,12,Fsome changeable or more unsettled
OL,13,Fconditions developing later in the
OL,14,Fperiod, with a risk of some heavy and
OL,15,Fthundery showers. Temperatures are
OL,16,Flikely to be above normal, with a
OL,17,Fgreater than normal chance of hot
OL,18,Fconditions developing at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
